    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏是我们UE5线上课8期的Houdini程序化生成案例，我们在Houdini中制作了迷宫关卡的生成管线，通过HDA在虚幻中添加场景、道具、陷阱等内容。这个游戏我们制作在周期1个月左右，主要目的还是想给大家展示一下迷宫组件的多样性，希望大家可以喜欢我们的小游戏~！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·迎战各种怪物<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244490/extras/efe099d8b5909e0e81b79e6c4b369e42.avif?t=1728550924\" width=512 height=286 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244490/extras/091fdbc5160b06fcb0de6c6ae7111dcb.avif?t=1728550924\" width=512 height=286 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·探索和收集</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244490/extras/676fc29e38c1ebe7635d0ca61bdd295e.avif?t=1728550924\" width=512 height=288 /></span></p>",
